<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="articles/finance/fixed-assets/150-percent-reducing-balance-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/fixed-assets/150-percent-reducing-balance-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91">Typically, when the amount that is calculated by using the 150% reducing balance depreciation method becomes less than the amount that would be calculated by using the straight line method, there is a conversion to the straight line method for the remaining life.</p>
